=Description=

The Center, however, is a grassroots effort by the entire bitcoin community in Korea to make bitcoin more visible and useful for the general public. The success of the Center comes from the community’s passion to create a better currency and payment system where anyone in the world can participate.
*Bitcoin ATM: Buy and Sell Bitcoins Easily
*Bitcoin for Beginners
*Remittance: Send Money Back Home
*Co-Working Space
*Conference Space
*Bitcoin Indie Market
*Merchant Directory

